title: Any Jungle Tips?
body: I am a Jungle main, in very low elo, and i would like to climb as fast as possible. Does anyone out there have any tips for me as a jungler? My main champions are Nunu, Master Yi and Xin Zhao. Any help is greatly appreciated. Thank You.

replies.body: Come add me. I main jg yi carrying myself to gold 1 right now, gonna hit plat soon, maybe even diamond
